text: Maryan Synakowski (14 March 1936 – 25 January 2021) was a French footballer. He played as a centre back. Synakowski played for Olympique Saint-Quentin, Sedan-Torcy B, Sedan-Torcy, Stade Français, Union Saint-Gilloise, Reims and Sedan. He played for the French national team between 1961 and 1965. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Footballers from Pas-de-Calais
